Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We finally arrived at the final battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The temple of Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a place that holds trapped souls from over a time span of 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner... Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will stop Dartz and his desires without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we will free everyone's souls in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba... We have to go all out in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Tragedy of Atlantis"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Water Metropolis, Atlantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlantis was a remarkable city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long before I ruled over the land as king,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its citizens received their strength from the Earth and from the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we began to spontaneously grow, we became a bountiful metropolis seemingly overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there, without a care in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nor greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we were at last content.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a massive, black dragon appeared and swallowed the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Orichalcos was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So something buried deep within the globe led to its advancement...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos gave our planet an enormous treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that is what we thought at {\i1}first{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because all of our energy, necessities and industrial goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything we used began depending on that miraculous substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I took the throne as king, the civilization of Atlantis entered a period of advancement beyond imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I did not notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor did my father, Ironheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly and slowly... The hearts of my citizens began to become corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're related to Ironheart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying this "Orichalcos" began to corrupt the hearts of the citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desire to satisfy oneself comes with it great irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within lies a breeding ground for the darkness of a person's heart to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No different than the people of today's society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pollution has spread all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distracted by the convenience of modern technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people have forgotten the importance of communication between the Earth and the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up their faith for modern beliefs, the people have begun to lose all emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity knows not the limitations of their cruelty towards nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are faced with conflict...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as their peace is suddenly brought to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiyori! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why has this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized everything in an instant...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos was not meant as a miraculous source of technology!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, it cultivates the darkness within the hearts of human beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and after consuming them,\N new life is created from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos is a cursed substance that was created in order to test this planet and the human beings that inhabit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To test human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings shall destroy themselves by the very same darkness that plagues their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos is but a substance that hastens the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz! You must throw away the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has changed our civilization...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that is of no concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must live among the spirits as we did long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must return to the traditions of the past, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is too late now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we were to abandon the Orichalcos, those infected would not return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, I have come up with a verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For I have heard the voice of this planet from within the Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it that human beings alone are\N blessed with that called "wisdom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why is it that very same "wisdom" exceeded itself, resulting in "imagination"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is because... the people of this planet require such gifts in order to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Earth sent Orichalcos in order to test its inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the end result of that test was failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As such, Earth granted me a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am to usher in the God of Orichalcos' descent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and send these frivolous humans to their demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After which, I am to create new human beings from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A mission of such aptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I have been handed this power in order to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to ensure the advent of the Orichalcos God, I require an abundance of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you gone mad, Dartz...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are to begin a spiritual ceremony crossing the very voids of history!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We aim to call forth the God of Orichalcos within our planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we seek help from the spirits from our previous era,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they are bound to grant us their strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This must be the link to the Spirit World!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O Divine Spirits! Please grant us power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They foolishly pleaded for the Spirits' aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They borrowed the power of what you have come to know as "Duel Monsters",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as they defied me and sought my destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the battle at the Stone Wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly after, my father sealed the door to the Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any of the remaining spirits' souls were locked away in various locations around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long period of 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the world began to rot all over again as human beings repeated the same mistakes they did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I once again aimed to call forth the God of Orichalcos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I decided to destroy the remaining traces of those Duel Monsters vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've already been defeated by the attack of our Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point forward, you shall personally experience my power first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Dartz's Life wasn't affected at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Orichalcos Kyutora's Special Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It holds the power to make all damage done onto me through a Monster's strike in battle zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...! Even though that was my brother's and Yugi's most powerful attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means he takes no damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Gigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Kaiba! That Monster increases its Attack Power whenever it's destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh... Seto... It is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you are capable of defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am unable to draw another card due to the Effect of Orichalcos Gigas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can activate this card from my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next form of power born\N from the blackest of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Deuteros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the second barrier of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "second" barrier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Deuteros...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As per the effects of this boundary,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Life is replenished by 500 points for every Monster I control on the field during every one of my turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold two Monsters on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I receive a 1000 point restoration to my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a Life Restoration barrier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, Orichalcos Gigas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Declare an attack against Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna use a 1400 Attack Monster to attack the 5000 Attack Master of Dragon Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, Orichalcos Gigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invoke the Effect of Orichalcos Kyutora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I receive no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! The bastard {\i1}purposely{\i0} attacked with Orichalcos Gigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so he could raise its Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even if he continues to increase Orichalcos Gigas' Attack Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Master of Dragon Knight's Attack Power is far beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks to me as if he's purposely trying to get us to attack that Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does it hold another Ability we're not aware of...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So long as that thing's here, we can't attack any of his other Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And even if we defeat that Orichalcos Gigas, it'll only come back with more Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must admit that it's a pretty formidable battle lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible for you to beat us in a direct assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one face-down card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I Summon Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I have one or fewer cards in my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Knight's Attack Power rises by 400 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you setting something up, Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, you only have one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I sacrifice the Monster I have in play in order to activate this Quick-Play Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Reflect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, go now! Use Master of Dragon Knight to attack him from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Reflect allows you to Direct Attack the enemy player!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From his blind spot over there, Orichalcos Kyutora can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack you with Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it! He's about to receive a 5000 Attack Power Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second... Barrier of Orichalcos is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second ability of Orichalcos Deuteros...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, by sacrificing a Monster on my side of the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...any attack will be nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in addition, the attacking Monster shall be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick-Play Magic! Fusion Cancel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you dodged it by a hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't even use Direct Attacks with the second barrier in play...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still have some of the mightiest Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know {\i1}all{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's weaknesses and their despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, the both of you are no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your greatest weaknesses lie within {\i1}yourselves{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Ritual Magic, Orichalcos Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send the Time Eater in my hand as an offering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which allows me to Special Summon Mirror Knight Calling from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, as a result of Mirror Knight Calling's Effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon "Mirror Knights" to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought four Monsters out at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at this moment in time, I hold six Monsters on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of Orichalcos Deuteros' effects, I regain 3000 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that is but the switch for the Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your greatest weaknesses lie within yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. The Attack Power of the Mirror Knights is determined by the Monsters they are facing in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they have the same Attack Points, then {\i1}his{\i0} Monsters should also be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those shields...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So long as they hold these shields...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Mirror Knights shall not be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as long as I have the Mirror Knight Calling,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their shields will continue to reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Life-Shaving Card Treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effects allow me to draw five new cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As per its risks, after five turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my entire hand is sent to the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Silent Death from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster from my Graveyard in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then sacrifice Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to Summon Kaiser Glider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser Glider is a card that cannot be destroyed when it battles against a Monster holding the same Attack Power it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you deserve a bit of credit for your quick thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Monsters are facing Monsters that automatically have the same Attack Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't act carelessly around them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Holy Barrier - Mirror Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Summon Big Shield Gardna in Defense Mode and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As per the effects of Orichalcos Deuteros, my Life will recover by 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Life rose above 10000...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Dartz... The next time you declare an attack, every single one of your Monsters will be destroyed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this moment to activate a Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy Mirror Knight Calling, the Immortality Ability of your Mirror Knights will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Destruction Ring!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the {\i1}hell{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?! Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} and Pegasus too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had activate Mirror Force, Partner and the others would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that you guys have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that every soul I have captured is under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four Mirror Knights Dartz Summoned were really the stolen souls of Yugi and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a low method to use against us, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the other Yugi can't attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} ignores the fact and aims to attack anyway, but the Mirror Knights protect one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to get out of this pinch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Captive Mirror Knights"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:23:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
